OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fbut cloudy in the north with late
OL,7,Fsunshine south then clear spells
OL,8,Falways more prolonged across southern
OL,9,FAberdeenshire. North winds
OL,10,Foccasionally fresh across the east
OL,11,Fcoast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA generally fair days weather
OL,14,Fin prospect with most dry with periods
OL,15,Fof sunshine widespread through the
OL,16,Fmorning, before turning hazy from the
OL,17,Fwest during the afternoon. Winds light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
